              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Custom voice cloning",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Generate personalized voices from as little as 10 seconds of reference audio, with support for emotional tone adjustments."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Multi-language synthesis",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Native support for over 20 languages, including English, Mandarin, and Spanish, with phoneme-level control for pronunciation accuracy."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Real-time streaming",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Audio chunks delivered via WebSocket for applications requiring immediate playback, such as live customer service bots."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Under the hood, the 12Hz sampling rate reduces computational overhead compared to higher-rate models, while the 1.7B parameters ensure vocal naturalness. This balance makes it suitable for high-throughput scenarios where latency budgets are tight—typically under 200ms for end-to-end synthesis."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For teams building interactive voice response (IVR) systems or audiobook platforms, these capabilities translate to reduced development time. The API abstracts away model management, letting you focus on integration rather than infrastructure."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
