      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Qwen3 TTS excels in low-latency scenarios and cost efficiency for high-volume use. However, if you need higher sample rates for audiophile applications, alternatives may be preferable. For voice cloning speed, Qwen3's 10-second requirement is notably aggressive."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Troubleshooting Common Issues"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Common errors include authentication failures, rate limiting, and invalid voice IDs. Here's how to address them:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "HTTP 401 Unauthorized",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Verify API key permissions and region settings. Rotate keys quarterly for security."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "HTTP 429 Too Many Requests",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Implement exponential backoff. The API returns a "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Retry-After",
                    "code": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " header; respect it to avoid temporary bans."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "HTTP 400 Bad Request",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Validate JSON schema against the "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "a",
                    "url": "https://docs.qwen3.com/tts/schema",
                    "title": null,
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "API specification"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ". Use tools like JSON Schema Validator."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "blockquote",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Warning:",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Voice IDs are case-sensitive and region-locked. A voice created in "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "us-east-1",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " cannot be used in "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "eu-west-1",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " without replication, which incurs additional latency."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For persistent issues, consult the "
          },
          {
            "type": "a",
            "url": "https://status.qwen3.com",
            "title": null,
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Qwen3 Status Page"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " for incident reports. Enable debug logging in the SDK to capture request/response details."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Deploying at Scale: Best Practices"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For production deployment, adopt these patterns to ensure reliability:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Use connection pooling",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Reuse HTTP connections to reduce handshake overhead. The SDK supports this via "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "client = qwen3_tts.Client(pool_connections=10)",
                    "code": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Implement circuit breakers",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Tools like Hystrix can prevent cascade failures during API outages."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Monitor key metrics",
                    "bold": true
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Track latency percentiles, error rates, and character usage with Prometheus and Grafana."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Security is paramount: encrypt API keys at rest, use IAM roles for cloud deployments, and audit access logs regularly. For global reach, deploy across multiple regions and use latency-based routing."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrating the Qwen3 TTS CustomVoice API into your production stack requires careful attention to latency, cost, and error handling. Start by benchmarking with your typical text samples, then iterate on caching and batching strategies to optimize expenses. For advanced voice customization, explore the "
